<dd><p>將原本的倉儲新增為遠端，並取名為「upstream」</p></dd>
<dt><a class="co" id="callout_github_CO2-2" href="ch00/co_github_CO2-2"><img src="/book/en/v2/book/06-github/../../callouts/2.png" alt="2"></a></dt>
